1
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:42,450
It's you,

2
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:44,500
Sister Hua.

3
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:47,170
I came here today to tell you

4
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,570
that Feifei is Dailing.

5
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:52,280
When she was pushed off the boat by Angwei,

6
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:54,320
I was the one who saved her downstream.

7
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:56,380
I felt sorry for what happened to her,

8
00:00:57,120 --> 00:00:59,120
so I decided to help her get revenge.

9
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,290
Sister Hua, you coming to see me

10
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:03,360
isn't just

11
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,000
to tell a story, is it?

12
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:08,320
I've already found out about all these things.

13
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,520
I originally planned

14
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:13,000
to have Dailing stay close to Angwei

15
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:15,000
to look for evidence from back then.

16
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,800
Angwei has always suspected her identity,

17
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:20,010
so he used various methods to test her.

18
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,480
Obviously,

19
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:25,289
Dailing has softened towards Angwei.

20
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:29,980
She forgot how she was pushed down back then,

21
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,240
and how miserably

22
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,650
her mother died.

23
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:38,720
She's hurting herself

24
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,780
to stay by his side,

25
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:42,050
without even realizing it.

26
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:43,320
Are you saying

27
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,039
that Dailing's old feelings for Angwei

28
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,479
have rekindled?

29
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,800
I'm a bit worried about that,

30
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,960
but what worries me more is that

31
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,620
if she stays by Angwei's side,

32
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:57,740
she will arouse Danpa's suspicion sooner or later.

33
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,640
Danpa

34
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,480
is a demon.

35
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,560
Even Chen Qian died at his hands.

36
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,660
You mean Angwei's mother,

37
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,479
Chen Qian?

38
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:15,000
When I received a mission to go to the Chen family back then,

39
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,160
I saw with my own eyes

40
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,820
that Danpa pushed Chen Qian downstairs.

41
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,680
Afterwards, Chen Qian's death was disguised as suicide.

42
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,400
But I knew

43
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:25,040
that Chen Qian found out Dai Haibo's death

44
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,900
was not an accident, but a murder,

45
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,000
so she was silenced by Danpa.

46
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,800
Are you saying

47
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:37,280
that Dailing's father was killed by Danpa?

48
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:39,760
Yes.

49
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,120
Then why didn't you tell Dailing

50
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:45,060
that the murderer of her father is Danpa?

51
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:50,160
I originally wanted to get rid of Danpa for Dailing myself.

52
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:52,420
I didn't want her to bear too much hatred.

53
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:53,940
Her mother's death

54
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,960
has already caused her enough pain.

55
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,120
If she finds out now

56
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,880
that there's a hidden truth behind her father's death,

57
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:02,010
I'm afraid she won't be able to take it.

58
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,160
You came to me.

59
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,920
Does she know?

60
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,120
She doesn't need to know.

61
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:11,760
Mr. Ou,

62
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,720
now only you can help her.

63
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,120
After all,

64
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:19,480
you were the only one who didn't hurt her back then.

65
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:20,160
I believe

66
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:22,290
with your feelings for her,

67
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,320
you must be willing to help her.

68
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:25,720
Right?

69
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,280
Of course I will help her.

70
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,290
I will help her even if it costs my life.

71
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,240
But I think no matter how cruel the truth is,

72
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:35,040
Dailing has the right to know it.

73
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,180
I don't agree with you,

74
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,800
but that's not the point.

75
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,040
The most important thing right now

76
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,700
is to get Dailing away from Angwei immediately.

77
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,930
What do you need me to do?

78
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,600
I don't care what method you use.

79
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,640
Whether it's kidnapping or imprisonment,

80
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,440
make Dailing immediately

81
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,240
leave Angwei's side.

82
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,480
Mr. Ou,

83
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,340
this is exactly what you want too.

84
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:58,970
Isn't it?

85
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:32,640
Okay.

86
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,040
How can I help you?

87
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,600
My boyfriend had a necklace

88
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,000
custom-made for me here.

89
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,520
I want to check its authenticity.

90
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,480
Well, miss,

91
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,040
all jewelry

92
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,440
custom-made by Tangong Jewelry

93
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,760
has a serial number on it.

94
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,120
With the serial number, you can check

95
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,360
its authenticity on our official website,

96
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,420
along with all transaction records.

97
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:22,640
Thank you.

98
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,120
So this necklace

99
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:50,360
was bought by Angwei for 500,000.

100
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,680
Then he...

101
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,320
Dailing,

102
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,160
don't leave me again.

103
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:07,240
Is his gentleness towards me now

104
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,120
real?

105
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,560
Why did Master Angwei bring me here?

106
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,290
Is this place

107
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,650
familiar to you?

108
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,040
I remember the first time

109
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,600
we met.

110
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,880
You said you liked butterflies.

111
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,700
What are you doing?

112
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,400
You were secretly taking pictures of me, weren't you?

113
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,130
Give it back.

114
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,480
There are plenty of people who want to take pictures of me,

115
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,240
but you're the first one to be so blatant

116
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,680
and arrogant about it.

117
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:56,740
Open it.

118
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,720
See for yourself.

119
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,540
I was taking a picture of a butterfly.

120
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,370
But that's still me.

121
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,880
That's just the corner of your shirt.

122
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,210
I bought these clothes,

123
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,600
so I have the portrait rights.

124
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,930
Nonsense. Give it to me.

125
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,480
What's your name?

126
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,720
Why should I tell you?

127
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:21,680
What?

128
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,120
What is your name?

129
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,200
Dailing.

130
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,080
Okay, I got it.

131
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,440
I don't understand what you're saying.

132
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:52,810
Then tell me.

133
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:57,200
What's your relationship with Sister Hua?

134
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,480
Who is Sister Hua?

135
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,040
The day I went to check your room,

136
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,960
she was there too, right?

137
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,210
The surveillance shows

138
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,640
she has been here more than once.

139
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,800
Did I tell you

140
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,820
not to bring outsiders in?

141
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,480
It took me half a month of investigation to find out

142
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,880
that she's a mercenary.

143
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,400
And there is

144
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,340
some kind of force behind her.

145
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,740
She is a dangerous person.

146
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,520
You'd better stay away from her.

147
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,770
Why are you here?

148
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:46,650
Miss Feifei.

149
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,090
Why I'm here,

150
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,560
you should know best.

151
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:52,960
Ang Wei.

152
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:56,410
Don't think that with just a contract,

153
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:58,380
you can claim someone as your own.

154
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,970
I failed to protect her five years ago.

155
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,080
Now,

156
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,360
I want to protect her.

157
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,780
Ou Shaowen.

158
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,660
You couldn't protect her five years ago.

159
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,940
You'll still be a loser in five years.

160
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,400
At least I have a contract with her.

161
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,160
And you?

162
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,960
You have nothing.

163
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:20,880
I admit it.

164
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,440
I am a loser.

165
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:24,020
What about you?

166
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,170
What are you?

167
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,600
A murderer?

168
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,440
Or are you someone

169
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,120
seeking redemption?

170
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:33,320
Ang Wei.

171
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,160
You know exactly

172
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,760
what you're doing right now.

173
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:39,600
You just can't let go of your obsession with Dailing.

174
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,460
If she says she is not Dailing now,

175
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:44,380
then everything you're doing is just an excuse.

176
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,380
Do you dare to admit it?

177
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,000
So what if she is Dailing?

178
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,690
So what if she is Feifei?

179
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,460
I told you I wouldn't restrict your freedom.

180
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,500
You choose.

181
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:01,680
Feifei.

182
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,290
I was stupid five years ago.

183
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:07,000
But now I just want to stand by your side.

184
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,480
No matter who you are,

185
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,480
what your name is,

186
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,200
or what your identity is.

187
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,240
The two of you,

188
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:23,170
one uses me as an excuse for atonement,

189
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:27,610
and the other treats me as an unforgettable substitute.

190
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,690
Have you ever respected me?

191
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,130
Have you?

192
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,250
But at least for now,

193
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:47,140
I have signed a contract with Mr. Ang Wei,

194
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,410
and I am his private secretary.

195
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,090
Let's go.

196
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,680
I don't care what method you use,

197
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:18,610
be it kidnapping or imprisonment.

198
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:22,000
Get Dailing away from Angwei immediately.

199
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,240
Mr. Ou.

200
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,980
This is exactly what you want,

201
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:26,650
isn't it?

202
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,320
I do love Dailing.

203
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,980
And I want her to leave Angwei too.

204
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,460
But I can't do that.

205
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,000
I can't use such despicable means.

206
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,330
Is this the time to talk about principles?

207
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:46,120
If Dailing stays by Angwei's side like this,

208
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,450
she'll only sink deeper

209
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,040
and eventually lose her life.

210
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:49,770
Don't worry.

211
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:53,090
I will definitely protect her.

212
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,570
I will protect her even if it costs my life.

213
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:58,290
But I can't use such despicable means.

214
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:00,620
Especially in front of the one I love.

215
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,040
It seems

216
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,040
it is time.

217
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,520
Let's meet, Dailing.

218
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,600
About your father's death.
